data.description: Sellers are offering $5K allowance to use as you choose! Come check out this beautiful home that is ready for a new homeowner! You will immediately see the care and love put into this home from the moment you arrive and see the freshly painted exterior and recently replaced roof. Once inside, you will see your over-sized living room featuring vaulted ceilings and a straight line of sight to the fully fenced in backyard. A well thought-out split floorplan gives everyone their private space but allows everyone to come together in the main areas. Your large, level backyard is sure to please anyone that loves to entertain featuring a deck, firepit area, and additional storage. Additionally, an electrical post placed perfectly for festive lights, grilling, or even install and enjoy a pool! This home is perfectly positioned to allow for a ton of natural light throughout each room creating a warm and inviting feeling to the home.
